data.meta_description: Pottawattamie County Map: 1875 Plan of Council Bluffs
data.text:
1875 Plan of Council Bluffs

Colored lithographed map. Shows wards, tracts, block numbers, radial distances from court house, etc. Relief shown by hachures.

Plan of Council Bluffs, Pottawattamie Co., State of Iowa. Chas. Shober & Co., props., Chicago Lith. Co.

(Published by the Andreas Atlas Co., Lakeside Building, Chicago, Ills.

Engraved & printed by Chas. Shober & Co., Props. of Chicago Lithographing Co.). 1875.
